### Create conversation
POST http://localhost:3000/api/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Conversation"
}

### List conversations
GET http://localhost:3000/api/conversations

### Load conversation
GET http://localhost:3000/api/conversations/<PUT-ID-HERE>


### Delete conversation
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/conversations/e0444c0092508a14
